Kittyeyes: Oh, nothing serious happened, got totally rejected by Roger just now, that's all.
Kittyeyes: No big deal~
Kittyeyes: Koll, I'm so thankful I still have you by my side...
Kittyeyes: Can't keep sulking like this...
Kittyeyes: I'm going to go pick some flowers to decorate my room. Koll, you wanna come along?
Kittyeyes: What? You want me to stay here; you'll go pick the flowers for me?
Koll: Wooo~
Kittyeyes: Is that so...
Kittyeyes: Alright then, I'll take your word for it.
Jeff: ...*cough*...*cough*...Koll...our men have betrayed us. They even got Kittyeyes. They're running away in the direction of the village; I can't stop them.
Jeff: You need to go save Kittyeyes now...*cough*...
Koll: RAAARRGGHH~~
Irritated Henchman: Damnit, this stinkin wolf again. Kill it; don't let it get in the way!
Betraying Henchman: Idiot, just take Kittyeyes away. She's our trump card against Roger.
Fearful Henchman: G-Get out of our way. Stop messing with our business!
Koll: AROOOOOOOO~~~
Fearful Henchman: W-W-Why is it on fire!?
Betraying Henchman: A wolf that bears raging flames...
Betraying Henchman: Isn't that a Glimmer Wolf, the one gramps used to talk about seeing when he was a kid? Aren't they supposed to be extinct?
Fearful Henchman: HELP, I surrender! Please stop...I give up. I give up!
Male Villager: Somebody help put out the fire! My kids are still in there!
Koll: AROOOOOOOO~~~
？？？: ... Please...stop...
Kittyeyes: ...Calm down, Koll...yes, that's a good boy. You don't have to be scared, everything's ok now.
Kittyeyes: Let's go home together...
Kittyeyes: ... I'm so glad you're back to normal again...
Roger: Koll, how dare you harm Kittyeyes! Have you gone insane!?
Kittyeyes: No, this has nothing to do with Koll...
Koll: Woo...
